    "Id": "chassisdef_valiant_VLT-3E",
    "Name": "Valiant",
    "Details": "Developed for The Republic of the Sphere, this Valiant uses a composite internal structure and XL gyro to save weight. The design is protected by five and a half tons of heavy ferro-fibrous armor. The MASC, hatchet, and small shield were replaced with a LAC/5 and a fluid gun, each with a ton of ammunition, while a targeting computer improves weapon accuracy.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Short</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.99</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Upper</color>",
